<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#5dd6f784231c5ab1ad1d1a60dbc00b4a>.
<#5dd6f784231c5ab1ad1d1a60dbc00b4a> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
