    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://doi.org/10.15468/KLLKYL>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-03-16T06:32:22.156Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
