    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://catalog.gavle.se/store/1/resource/149>, <https://catalog.gavle.se/store/1/resource/151>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/provenance> _:b0__4069.
_:b0__4069 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "The objects are measured photogrammetrically."@en, "Objekten är fotogrammetriskt framtagna."@sv;
