<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#4f01a694349c034bb1b8d31372f57595>.
<#4f01a694349c034bb1b8d31372f57595> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://api.kolada.se/v3/kpi/U72203>;
