<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#a4f739c6bc36b4b87b8cbbdbab7521f6>.
<#a4f739c6bc36b4b87b8cbbdbab7521f6> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
