<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#155e379a750a4fcc366813fc31511310>.
<#155e379a750a4fcc366813fc31511310> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://doi.org/10.5878/cnd4-fs77>;
